		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />For me it's rather lack of inspiration... I have no idea how to draw any enemies so they look fun but still are interesting to fight (no have the player just press the B button several times without thinking).
<br />
<br />I have completed a working game engine for Dragon Skill, the only thing lacking right now is how to detect the end of a stage and a few of the latter player attacks I'm planning to do. The real problem is that I have serious trouble implementing the enemies and their AI. I have made almost no progress for the last 5 months.

		

