<br />Well, I've spent the past few weeks/hundreds of hours getting the SNES APU's DSP RE'd down to the cycle level, every last detail of operation. During this I've developed more effective ways of writing automated tests that can all run from one ROM, which should allow more NES test ROMs written in this new style. I'm kind of eager to port this from SPC-700/65816 asm back to the NES.

		

